body:
# Welcome!

Although it might be a bad idea to hand edit this into IE9, it's all about getting work done with the tools at hand, so here goes!

## Why now?
I've had an account for quite a while, and am just now (10/30/15) creating a personal page, from IE 9 even... so, why? 

Well, I am learning so much recently as I dive back into Python, that I wanted to start writing about all that I am reading somewhere, and this seems to be a great place to start.

## Whoami?

@mgrollins
